snippet.title: The Raven Project gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for The Raven Project, Dos PC game produced by Cryo Interactive in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/the-raven-project/8081/
Flying around blasting bad guys in this science fiction on-rails shooter.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
